name: Still Fractals - The Oblivion of Menger
description:
Resolution: 1080x1080

Fractal from a large collection. I make them as I see them.
Made with Blender and my own in-house toolkit developed in 2021.

My deepest gratitude goes to Benoit Mandelbrot, Gaston Julia and all those who contributed to making visualization of fractal possible.

Part of the proceeds from the sale will go to the Blender Development Fund.
